These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, classical
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, azure
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, grapes
1. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the fan of classical is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | gospel   |
| Color         | azure | orange |
| Food     | kiwi | grapes    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
City: san-francisco, miami
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
2 different games are played: billiard, bridge
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, blue
1. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person who likes blue##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| City          | san-francisco     | miami |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Game           | bridge         | billiard     |
| Color     | purple   | blue    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, magic-tricks
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, azalea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby    | magic-tricks     | drawing |
| Flower         | azalea | dahlia    |
| Sport         | tennis         | rugby        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

