There 2 different types of food: cabbage, strawberry
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, hiking
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the person eating strawberry is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing chess is the person eating cabbage##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Game           | chess | domino    |
| Food   | cabbage       | strawberry |
| Hobby           | woodworking         | hiking    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

