.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-10::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, july
There 2 different types of food: banana, papaya
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, havana
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person eating banana##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Birthday      | july | march       |
| Food          | banana   | papaya    |
| Game           | chess   | mah-jongg |
| Cigar   | havana      | montecristo    |

