The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike
1. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the project-manager is in an even position##4
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Job           | accountant | project-manager |
| Cigar   | bluemaster    | bolivar      |
| Flower           | sunflower      | tulip          |
| Transport         | quad-bike | jet-ski       |

